<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Plant Recognition</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq7V2FOQKf5fzQmZUu9gT0j/c5GL/FB2Fmdns1b6S2Ys/kS0H9IODG5K2" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        .intro-container {
            background-color: #323030;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            text-align: center;
            width: 15%;
            top: 70px;
            left: 20px;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .paragraph-component {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
            position: fixed;
            top: calc(70px + 20px + 60px);
            left: 20px;
            right: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #3c3b3b;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .recent_sightings {
            background-color: #323030;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            text-align: center;
            top: 380px;
            left: 20px;
            width: 15%;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .image-box {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border: 2px dashed #cccccc;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 18px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 250px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="navbar d-flex flex-column align-items-center pt-3 position-relative">
        <%- include('navbar.ejs') %>
    </header>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('image-input').addEventListener('change', function(event) {
            var input = event.target;
            var label = document.getElementById('image-label');

            if (input.files && input.files[0]) {
                label.textContent = input.files[0].name;
                previewImage(event);
            } else {
                label.textContent = 'Add/insert an image';
            }
        });

        function previewImage(event) {
            var input = event.target;
            var preview = document.getElementById('image-preview');

            if (input.files && input.files[0]) {
                var reader = new FileReader();

                reader.onload = function (e) {
                    preview.src = e.target.result;
                    preview.style.display = 'block'; // Show the image preview
                };

                reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
            }
        }
    </script>

    <div class="intro-container">
        <div class="Intro"> Introduction Text </div>
    </div>

    <div class="paragraph-component">
        <p>Classifying organisms based on similarities helps provide order tothe thousands of living organisms on earth.
        Plant biologists have described various situations in which plants exhibit different behaviours based on identity.
        Plant identification tool helps you discover the names and care needs of any houseplant, garden variety, or wildflower.
        Explore our extensive plant database and find the perfect fit for your needs.
        Explore by name, image, or browse curated collections.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="recent_sightings">
        <div class="sighting"> Recent Sightings</div>
    </div>

    <div class="image-section">
        <div class="image-box">
            <input type="file" id="image-input" accept="image/*" style="display: none;">
            <label for="image-input" id="image-label">Add/insert an image</label>
            <img id="image-preview" src="#" alt="Image Preview" style="display: none;">
        </div>
    </div>
<main>





</main>

</body>
</html>